org.orgName: The District Court of the United States

div1.p: FORM NO.282 RETURN ON SERVICE OF WRIT
United States of America Western Dristict of Washington,} ss:

I hereby certify and return that I served the annexed Hebeas Corpus, on the therin-named King Dykeman, Judge, Seattle Washington, by handing to and leaving a true and correct copy therof with King Dykeman personally at SeattleWash, in said District on the 26th, day of October, A.D. 1916
Unites States District Court Western DISTRICT OF WASHIINGTON NO.3451
In the Matter of Application of Mrs. Gladys Fredrika Fuson For Writ of Habeas corpus
Let the within Writ Issues - - - - - - - - - - U.S. District Judge
Return and filed this day of A.D. 189 Clerk By Deputy Clerk
FILED IN THE U.S. District Court Western Dist. of Washington, NORTHERN DIVISION OCT 26 1916 FRANK L.CROSBY, Clerk By Edm Lakim Deputy
